{"postId":7572212,"headline":"","publishedAt":"2024-09-06T16:50:00.780Z","state":1,"cws":[],"tags":["art","original art","original character","reference sheet","css","digital art"],"blocks":[{"type":"markdown","markdown":{"content":"<h1 style=\"padding:0;margin:0;box-sizing:border-box;margin-bottom:1rem;text-align:center\">OC's Reference &amp; Info</h1>\n<p id=\"disclaimer\" style=\"padding:0;margin:0;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:center;margin-bottom:1rem;opacity:0.7\">Note: the body reference of the characters can be seen by scrolling their images horizontally, but keep in mind that they are depicted semi-naked.</p>\n<details open=\"\" style=\"padding:0;margin:0;box-sizing:border-box;border-radius:1rem;background-color:rgba(59,126,80,0.5);border:2px rgb(59,126,80) solid\">\n  <summary style=\"margin:0;box-sizing:border-box;font-size:1.5rem;font-weight:bold;border-radius:1rem;text-align:center;padding:0.5rem\"><span style=\"padding:0;margin:0;box-sizing:border-box\"><!--ps=2-->Saulo Oliveira</span></summary>\n  <div style=\"margin:0;box-sizing:border-box;display:flex;flex-direction:row;padding:0 0.5rem 0.5rem 0.5rem;justify-content:space-between\">\n    <div style=\"padding:0;margin:0;box-sizing:border-box;border:2px dashed;border-radius:1rem;box-shadow:0 0 5px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5);height:auto;display:flex;flex-direction:row;overflow:scroll hidden;scroll-snap-type:x mandatory;max-width:calc(35% - 0.5rem);object-fit:scale-down;max-height:350px;border-color:rgb(59,126,80);background-color:rgba(59,126,80,0.5)\">\n        <img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/1HjtIoD.png\" style=\"padding:0;margin:0;box-sizing:border-box;aspect-ratio:auto;scroll-snap-align:start;object-fit:scale-down\">\n        <img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/4xGtMu6.png\" style=\"padding:0;margin:0;box-sizing:border-box;aspect-ratio:auto;scroll-snap-align:start;object-fit:scale-down\">\n    </div>\n    <div style=\"margin:0;box-sizing:border-box;border:2px dashed;border-radius:1rem;box-shadow:0 0 5px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5);height:auto;width:65%;display:flex;flex-direction:column;align-items:center;padding:0.5rem 0.5rem;overflow:auto;max-height:350px;border-color:rgb(59,126,80);background-color:rgba(59,126,80,0.5)\">\n      <details open=\"\" style=\"padding:0;margin:0;box-sizing:border-box;border-radius:1rem\">\n      <summary style=\"padding:0;margin:0;box-sizing:border-box;font-weight:bold;text-align:center;font-size:1.25rem\">Basic Info</summary>\n      <p style=\"padding:0;margin:0;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:center\">male (he/him) - 23yo - 1.70m - florist</p>\n      </details>\n      <details style=\"padding:0;margin:0;box-sizing:border-box;border-radius:1rem\">\n      <summary style=\"text-align:center;padding:0;margin:0;box-sizing:border-box;font-weight:bold;font-size:1.25rem\">Description</summary>\n      <p style=\"padding:0;margin:0;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:center\">Saulo is a kind and cheerful florist. He's always smiling and trying to see the bright side of things. Some may say that he's superficial, but he's well aware of the complexities of life.</p>\n      <p style=\"padding:0;margin:0;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:center\">As a child, he spent most of his time in a hospital. And growing up, his excessive politeness and inability to grasp social clues made him unable to connect with people his age.</p>\n      <p style=\"padding:0;margin:0;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:center\">He's  graduated in Botanic and works alone in his floriculture. Although he's a great florist, he's bad dealing with money and managment. He wears the same dress shirt everyday as a uniform.</p>\n        <p style=\"padding:0;margin:0;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:center\">His hobbies are reading and craftwork.</p>\n      </details>\n      <details style=\"padding:0;margin:0;box-sizing:border-box;border-radius:1rem\">\n      <summary style=\"padding:0;margin:0;box-sizing:border-box;font-weight:bold;text-align:center;font-size:1.25rem\">Design Notes</summary>\n      <p style=\"padding:0;margin:0;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:center\">From left to right, his scars are from a heart surgery and pacemaker respectively. The internal margins of his dress shirt have olive branches sewn.</p>\n      <h4 style=\"padding:0;margin:0;box-sizing:border-box;margin-bottom:0.5rem;text-align:center\">Colors</h4>\n      <div style=\"padding:0;margin:0;box-sizing:border-box;border-radius:0.5rem;overflow:hidden;display:flex;flex-direction:row;width:100%;height:2rem;box-shadow:0 0 5px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5);aspect-ratio:auto\">\n        <div style=\"background-color:#37413b;padding:0;margin:0;box-sizing:border-box;width:100%\"></div>\n        <div style=\"background-color:#3b7e50;padding:0;margin:0;box-sizing:border-box;width:100%\"></div>\n        <div style=\"background-color:#9d4a3b;padding:0;margin:0;box-sizing:border-box;width:100%\"></div>\n        <div style=\"background-color:#c27f65;padding:0;margin:0;box-sizing:border-box;width:100%\"></div>\n        <div style=\"background-color:#6a2525;padding:0;margin:0;box-sizing:border-box;width:100%\"></div>\n        <div style=\"background-color:#260716;padding:0;margin:0;box-sizing:border-box;width:100%\"></div>\n        <div style=\"background-color:#1f2a4a;padding:0;margin:0;box-sizing:border-box;width:100%\"></div>\n        <div style=\"background-color:#575e74;padding:0;margin:0;box-sizing:border-box;width:100%\"></div>\n        <div style=\"background-color:#a0716f;padding:0;margin:0;box-sizing:border-box;width:100%\"></div>\n      </div>\n        </details>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n</details>"}},{"type":"markdown","markdown":{"content":"<p style=\"padding:0;margin:0;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:center\"><br style=\"padding:0;margin:0;box-sizing:border-box\">More to be added later.</p>"}},{"type":"markdown","markdown":{"content":"\n<!--\n59, 126, 80\n-->"}}],"pinned":true,"commentsLocked":false,"sharesLocked":false,"singlePostPageUrl":"https://cohost.org/NekoRaita/post/7572212-h1-style-padding-0"}